title: STITCHED 016 (2013) (Avatar) (4 Covers) (Darkness-Empire)
description:
Stitched #16

Tokyo entrepreneur Kenji Nakamura's revenge upon the yakuza clan begins with the supernatural assassins known as "the Stitched!" These creatures cannot be stopped by either physical force or modern weapons, but as Nakamura's plan to secure another recruit for his growing Stitched army proceeds, an even more horrifying entity manifests itself in his very home!

Available with a Regular, Wraparound, Gore, and special Slashed Incentive cover by series artist Fernando Furukawa.
